text: The 34th century BC was a century which lasted from the year 3400 BC to 3301 BC. ==Cultures== *Stage IIIa2 of the Naqada culture in Egypt (dated in 1998). *Archaic forms of cuneiform emerge in the late Uruk period in Mesopotamia. *Burial of a child at Ashleypark Burial Mound, Ireland (c. 3350 BC) ==Religion== * Enoch (c. 33hej ==References== -6 -66
